IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.containing an area of TWO THOUSAND FOURTEEN (2,014) SQUARE METERS , more or less. All corners marked P.S. cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 40 cms. Bearings true. Date of original survey, August 6, 1906 – July 1907 and that survey, executed by Geodetic Engineer, Benedicto A. Arjona on October 21, November 18, 1988 and March 20 – April 30, 1990 and approved on September 7, 1990.

Done, in the City of Manila, this 16th day of June in the year of our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

